Package imagingbook.common.ransac

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RandomDraw<T>
    Randomly draws a set of k unique, non-null elements from a given array with elements of type T, which may contain null elements.
    RansacCurveDetector<T extends Curve2d>
    Generic RANSAC detector for 2D curves.
    RansacCurveDetector.RansacParameters
    Parameters used by all RANSAC types.
    RansacCurveResult<T extends Curve2d>
    Represents a single detection result returned by an implementation of RansacCurveDetector.
    RansacDetectorCircle
    RANSAC detector for circles.
    RansacDetectorCircle.Parameters
    Nested class extending RansacCurveDetector.RansacParameters to specify additional RANSAC parameters.
    RansacDetectorEllipse
    RANSAC detector for ellipses.
    RansacDetectorEllipse.Parameters
    Nested class extending RansacCurveDetector.RansacParameters to specify additional RANSAC parameters.
    RansacDetectorLine
    RANSAC detector for straight lines.
    RansacDetectorLine.Parameters
    Nested class extending RansacCurveDetector.RansacParameters to specify additional RANSAC parameters.
